TY  - JOUR
TI  - Determination of Consumer Unit Scales
AU  - Singh, Balvir
AU  - Nagar, A. L.
AB  - [This paper develops an iterative procedure for estimating "specific" and "income" consumer unit scales in Engel curve analysis. The proposed procedure is essentially a modification of the Prais and Houthakker method and is illustrated by means of a numerical example based on the Indian National Sample Survey data.]
